If you have created file inside `App` then you should put `namespace App` at the top of the page.

    namespace App;

Namespace is the concept of PHP which is uses for creating files in namespace (or file in a folder which are written for same purpose)  and use it in a easy way instead of call using full path.

1. Create a `packages` folder in the root and add the package to another directory inside that folder. Suppose the path will be `packages/phpspellcheck`.
